LEGIONELLOSIS, LEGIONNAIRES - USA (PENNSYLVANIA) (02)
*****************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
Sponsored in part by Elsevier, publisher of
